# MemorySafe Benchmarks

This folder contains validation scripts and result summaries for evaluating the MemorySafe policy across heterogeneous continual learning benchmarks.

The goal of these experiments is to test **generalization of the memory governance policy** under increasing task complexity and data modality shifts.


