---

## Benchmarks Included

The same unchanged MemorySafe policy was evaluated on:

- MNIST  
- Fashion-MNIST  
- CIFAR-10  
- CIFAR-100  
- Omniglot  
- Permuted MNIST  
- PneumoniaMNIST (MedMNIST)

No dataset-specific tuning was applied.

---

## Metrics

We report:

- **Task-0 Protection**  
  Accuracy on the first task after learning all subsequent tasks.

- **Rare-Class Recall**  
  Recall on low-frequency or safety-critical classes.

- **Overall Accuracy**  
  Accuracy across all seen classes.

---

