| CIFAR-100      | 100%              | N/A         |
| Omniglot       | 100%              | N/A         |
| Permuted MNIST | 100%              | N/A         |
| PneumoniaMNIST | â€“                 | 0.917       |

These results indicate zero-shot generalization of a memory allocation policy across tasks, modalities, and difficulty regimes.

---

## Reproducibility

Each benchmark includes:

- fixed random seeds  
- identical policy parameters  
- identical memory capacity  

Scripts are designed to run on CPU or GPU.

This folder serves as the experimental evidence for claims reported in the MemorySafe documentation and website.

